---
description: Security-first development rules
globs:
  - src/**/*.tsx
  - src/**/*.ts
  - src/app/api/**/*.ts
alwaysApply: true
---

# Security Priority

- Security takes priority over convenience.
- Never expose sensitive data in console logs, client responses,
  or error messages.
- Authentication must always be verified server-side.
- Never trust client input.
- All financial actions require authenticated sessions.
